class=\"TextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\" lang=\"ES-ES\" xml:lang=\"ES-ES\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\">Marzo se considera un mes ca\u00f3tico con todo lo que se debe a realizar, y a\u00f1adamos el mito que ni\u00f1as y ni\u00f1os no desean volver a sus respectivos colegios. <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\">Sin embargo,<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\"> lo cierto, es que much<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\">as personas<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\"> esperan reencontrarse para asistir al <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\">lugar donde<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\"> aprenden y crecen <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\">sus<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW202448317 BCX8\"> sue\u00f1os.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW202448317 BCX8\" data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0d353f elementor-widget elementor-widget-ha-post-info happy-addon ha-post-info\" data-id=\"f0d353f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"ha-post-info.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"ha-inline-items ha-icon-list-items ha-post-info\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ha-icon-list-item elementor-repeater-item-5e0edbd ha-inline-item\" itemprop=\"datePublished\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/goodneighbors.cl\/2024\/03\/01\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ha-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-calendar\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M12 192h424c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v260c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V204c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12zm436-44v-36c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48h-48V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H160V12c0-6.6-